divs: Sighting DetailsI don't know if this is the place to put this but here goes... one early morning around 2 and 3 am my Rotty was laying next to my bed when I was awaken by her growling I reached for her in a sleepy stooper and she kept growling at the door. I rubbed my eyes and then looked at the door way and saw 3 heads there one took his hand and lifted it up and slowly brought it down all of a sudden my dogs stopped growing and she went to sleep and when I looked back up at them they blinked and did the same hand jester and I went to sleep... later that morning I woke with a very very bad head ache my Dog was very Quite and would not come out of my room... I had a small circle wound on my calf but I dont know how it got there... and that is all I remember on that, but after that encounter I have seen many sitings of UFOs to many to recall all of them... I do remember this one it was in the summer of 2001 I was in our Pool it was an over cast day, something made me feel like I needed to look up and when I did an oval shaped mettle object appeared from the clouds. The cloud cover was very low that day so the object was not very high so and I could see windows that went from one side to the other it made no sound, and it was moving very slowly between the clouds.
